<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Ice Comet Quest Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Talk to Sulgar in Everfrost to get the quest.<BR>
<BR>
2) Azia - found on the ocean floor in Erud's Crossing.<BR>
<BR>
3) Beza - found in the underwater caves.<BR>
<BR>
4) Dena - found in Dagnor's Cauldron near Kedge Keep.<BR>
<BR>
5) Ena - found in Lower Guk in the room with the reanimated hand.<BR>
<BR>
6) Fana - found in Oasis of Marr in the underwater tower.<BR>
<BR>
7) Geza - found in Highhold Pass in the water near one of the waterfalls.<BR>
<BR>
8) Heda - found in the Qeynos Aquaducts in the shark pit.<BR>
<BR>
9) Izah - found in Neriak Commons a bar called The Blind Fish.<BR>
<BR>
10) Jaka - Found in Unrest<BR>
<BR>
11) Once you have all the rods go back to Sulgar and get the container.  Combine the rods and you will receive staff of the wheel and star of eyes.   NOTE: You can fail in the combination even if you have the right components.</div>
