<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I did this at level 30 and am helping a lv 33 get through it now. Its possible to do this, but you have to accept you will prob die a couple of times. For example the gobs at oasis will kos when you grab the rod (invis till then), so ready yonder and gate, or go back for body later. As far as the Guk run, I paid a lv 48 cleric to get me in and gated out, also caught the time between hand spawns. <BR>
<BR>
Additional note: the C rod is in lake rath, in cave under back side of the ramp island, you will prob. need endure breath for this one. I took it from outside the tower and the gobs didnt agro on me.</font></td></tr></table>
